title: Blue Dive 2011
description:
Synopsis
As Selim, a diver bewitched by the sea, dies on a hospital bed, and as Mokhtar, a failed painter, contemplates on the color of death, Dalia, a nearby nurse, remembers her father's drowning. Set in the Mediterranean Alexandria, this is a story of a brief encounter which compares death to the sea.

CAST
Sayed Ragab
Donia Massoud
Atef Youssef
Written and Directed by: Mostafa Youssef

PRODUCTION
Produced by the Egyptian Film Center
Shooting Format: 35mm - 1:1.85 - Color
Previous Festivals: Official Selection International Film Festival Rotterdam. - Doha Tribeca Film Festival - Made In Med Film Competition
